# k6 Load Test Results

This directory stores k6 load test results in JSON format.

Results are generated by running:

```bash
k6 run --out json=results/<type>-<date>.json tests/load/k6-<type>-test.js
```

Files in this directory are gitignored (large JSON outputs).
Only the summary reports in `docs/LOAD-TEST-REPORT.md` are committed.
